title: Unibot Boosts Token Value With Solana Ecosystem Draw
description: UNIBOT holders are set to receive some 80% of the supply of Solana-based UNISOL through a snapshot and claim mechanism.

title: Bitcoin Longs Above $43K in Focus, Analyst Says
description: Bitcoin's wave 5 impulse move has begun and could see prices top $50,000 by the end of the first quarter, 10x Research's Markus Thielen said, having correctly predicted the recent pullback.
